OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT crowhunter        ~%kitid%~
OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT splinteringshot   ~%s1%~
OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT visceralattack    ~%s2%~
OUTER_TEXT_SPRINT crowhunterbleed   ~%s1%b~


